{
  "stem": "20142.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is the train to jump on [INAUDIBLE] if I would successfully cross underneath of the outdoor restrooms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, I have a striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They will recognize me very easily, no matter where I will go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said on the day that we-- you will decide that you have to go, you will have a hang-- hanging different coat and different pants.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had the number of-- mine was 14,284.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On my uniform on my chest, and on the side of the pants, with the two triangle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was red.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other one was yellow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The red was political.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the yellow was the Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was uniform of Star of David, so they were pinning on every Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was not starting to do political.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why you became political to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did not necessarily you had to be political.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every Jew was wearing red and yellow star.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how they could tell the Jew from the Gentile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the orders were having red-- the Polish people, Czech people, whoever came from other country to Majdanek-- get the red triangle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The larger part on top, and the triangle on the bottom, narrow part.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And above this was the number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the same thing was on the left side of the pant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this-- with a uniform like this, you couldn't get very far in Poland Somebody would have recognized you and turn you in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or the Germans would recognize you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you needed some other outfit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he simply said to me, there will be a little bit bigger than you can stand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But don't change it in the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Carry it over your head or underneath.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
